on P.K. Saenchai Muaythaigym]] || Omnoi Stadium || [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]] || Decision || 5 || 3:00\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=9 |{{small|Retains the Omnoi Stadium middleweight title.}}\n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2015-08-15 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|THA}} Rungrawee P.K. Saenchaimuaythaigym || Omnoi Stadium || [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]] || KO || 3 ||\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=9 |{{small|Wins the Omnoi Stadium middleweight title.}}\n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2015-03-07 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|THA}} Chenrob Pumpanmuang || Master of the Ring || [[Pattaya]], [[Thailand]] || Decision || 5 || 3:00\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=9 |{{small|Wins the Venum middleweight title.}}\n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 2015-02-01 || Loss ||align=left|{{flagicon|THA}} Kanongsuk Chuwattana || MAX Muay Thai, Tournament Semi-Finals || [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]] || Disqualification || 2 ||  \n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2014-11-09 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|SWE}} Tobias Alexandersson || MAX Muay Thai, Tournament Qualification Finals || [[Pattaya]], [[Thailand]] || Decision || 3 || 3:00 \n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2014-11-09 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|THA}} Fahmongkol Sor. Jor. Danrayong || MAX Muay Thai, Tournament Qualification Semi-Finals || [[Pattaya]], [[Thailand]] || Decision || 4 || 3:00 \n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2014-10-05 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|THA}} Kanongsuk Chuwattana || MAX Muay Thai || [[Pattaya]], [[Thailand]] || KO || 2 ||\n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n| 2014-09-28 || Win ||align=left|{{flagicon|CHN}} Sun Weiqiang || Wu Lin Feng || [[Hong Kong]] || Decision || 3 || 3:00 \n\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 2014-06-14 || Loss ||align=left|{{flagicon|THA}} [[Thongchai Sitsongpeenong]] || Best of Siam 5 || [[Pari