{"title_page": "2015 Canadian Junior Curling Championships \u2013 Men's tournament", "text_new": "{{main|2015 Canadian Junior Curling Championships}}\n{{Infobox curling\n| Name = 2015 Canadian Junior Curling Championships <br> Men's tournament\n| Logo =\n| Size =\n| Host city = [[Corner Brook, Newfoundland and Labrador|Corner Brook]], [[Newfoundland and Labrador]]\n| Arena = [[Corner Brook Civic Centre]] <br> [[Corner Brook Curling Club]]\n| Dates = January 24\u2013February 1\n| Winner = '''{{MB}}'''\n| Curling club = [[Deer Lodge Curling Club|Deer Lodge CC]], [[Winnipeg]]\n| Skip = [[Braden Calvert]]\n| Third = [[Kyle Kruz]]\n| Second = [[Lucas van den Bosch]]\n| Lead = [[Brendan Wilson]]\n| Finalist = {{SK}} ([[Jacob Hersikorn]])\n}}\nThe '''men's tournament''' of the '''2015 [[M&M Meat Shops]] [[Canadian Junior Curling Championships]]''' will be held from January 24 to February 1 at the [[Corner Brook Civic Centre]] and the [[Corner Brook Curling Club]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.curling.ca/2015juniors-en/2014/08/07/corner-brook-to-host-2015-mm-meat-shops-canadian-juniors/|title=Corner Brook to host 2015 M&M Meat Shops Canadian Juniors|date=7 August 2014|publisher=[[Canadian Curling Association]]}}</ref>\n\n==Teams==\nThe teams are listed as follows:\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Province !! Skip !! Third !! Second !! Lead !! Club(s)\n|-\n| {{AB}} || [[Karsten Sturmay]] || [[Tristan Steinke]] || [[Brett Winfield]] || Mac Lenton || Avonair CC, [[Edmonton, Alberta|Edmonton]]\n|-\n| {{BC}} || Paul Henderson || Duncan Silversides || Benton Boychuk-Chorne || Tim Henderson || [[Victoria Curling Club|Victoria CC]], [[Victoria, British Columbia|Victoria]]\n|-\n| {{MB}} || [[Braden Calvert]] || Kyle Kurz || Lucas van den Bosch || Brendan Wilson || [[Deer Lodge Curling Club|Deer Lodge CC]], [[Winnipeg, Manitoba|Winnipeg]]\n|-\n| {{NB}} || Ren\u00e9 Comeau || Andrew Burgess || Alex MacNeil || Ryan Freeze || [[Capital Winter Club|Capital WC]], [[Fredericton, New Brunswi